Because I felt bad.

516
00:32:00.418 --> 00:32:02.170
I'm sure you remember too.

517
00:32:02.837 --> 00:32:07.050
There was a case two years ago
where a teacher was murdered at school

518
00:32:07.133 --> 00:32:08.343
by their own student.

519
00:32:09.260 --> 00:32:12.180
I thought teachers' rights
needed to be clearly established

520
00:32:12.263 --> 00:32:14.057
so nothing like that happens again.

521
00:32:14.140 --> 00:32:15.892
But why Daehan High of all places?

522
00:32:15.975 --> 00:32:18.269
My son is suffering
because of it right now.

523
00:32:19.437 --> 00:32:21.606
Does your son go to Daehan High?

524
00:32:23.358 --> 00:32:24.442
Oh dear.

525
00:32:25.902 --> 00:32:27.612
The inspector has been going too far.

526
00:32:27.695 --> 00:32:30.448
If this is publicized.
public criticism will grow fierce.

527
00:32:30.531 --> 00:32:32.283
Nothing good can come from this.

528
00:32:32.367 --> 00:32:34.243
So why don't you just end it here?

529
00:32:37.246 --> 00:32:40.375
Well. there are a lot of eyes on us.

530
00:32:40.458 --> 00:32:43.294
and the organization
has just been established.

531
00:32:43.378 --> 00:32:45.672
How about we just wait a little longer?

532
00:32:45.755 --> 00:32:48.424
You know I have respect for you. Minister.

533
00:32:49.592 --> 00:32:51.803
I'm telling you all this for your sake.

534
00:32:51.886 --> 00:32:55.431
You wouldn't want to retire from politics
over something like this.

535
00:33:01.521 --> 00:33:03.314
A father would do anything

536
00:33:04.232 --> 00:33:05.817
for his child.

537
00:33:16.995 --> 00:33:19.455
This is Ryu Gwang-pil
of the Happiness Hope Party.

538
00:33:19.539 --> 00:33:21.332
Please support him.

539
00:33:21.958 --> 00:33:23.543
-Thank you.
-What's the time?

540
00:33:24.043 --> 00:33:25.420
Shouldn't he be here by now?

541
00:33:25.920 --> 00:33:28.631
-Come on. set your phones to vibrate.
-Sorry.

542
00:33:28.715 --> 00:33:31.467
<i>People as People. Politics as Politics</i>.

543
00:33:31.551 --> 00:33:34.220
What's this?
"Using aides for personal matters"?

544
00:33:34.303 --> 00:33:37.306
"Bribery in exchange
for local election nomination"?

545
00:33:38.016 --> 00:33:40.393
-Sexual harassment?
-What's this about?

546
00:33:40.476 --> 00:33:45.857
Ryu Gwang-pil!

547
00:33:45.940 --> 00:33:47.775
Thank you for taking the time to come.

548
00:33:47.859 --> 00:33:50.445
Do you admit to the bribery allegations?

549
00:33:50.528 --> 00:33:52.655
-What do you mean?
-There has been a tip-off.

550
00:33:52.739 --> 00:33:54.282
It's about your sexual misconduct.

551
00:33:54.866 --> 00:33:57.618
Is it true that you engaged
in illegal property speculation?

552
00:33:57.702 --> 00:33:59.078
What the hell is going on?

553
00:33:59.162 --> 00:34:00.872
I'll look into it. You should go.

554
00:34:00.955 --> 00:34:03.458
-Hurry and block them off here!
-Don't push!

555
00:34:03.541 --> 00:34:05.376
Do you admit it? Please say something!

556
00:34:05.460 --> 00:34:06.878
Assemblyman Ryu!

557
00:34:09.088 --> 00:34:10.423
Damn it.

558
00:34:48.252 --> 00:34:49.670
What's going on?

559
00:34:49.754 --> 00:34:51.130
It's noisy out there.

560
00:34:51.214 --> 00:34:52.840
There's no need for you to know.

561
00:34:53.591 --> 00:34:55.301
It'd be best if you left now.

562
00:34:57.261 --> 00:35:00.807
You must be a little slow on the uptake.

563
00:35:11.818 --> 00:35:12.777
Don't tell me

564
00:35:14.362 --> 00:35:16.072
you're behind this?

565
00:35:16.572 --> 00:35:18.783
Who put you up to this?

566
00:35:27.875 --> 00:35:29.836
It took me two years…

567
00:35:31.796 --> 00:35:33.172
to create the ERPB.

568
00:35:34.465 --> 00:35:35.716
It turns out

569
00:35:36.342 --> 00:35:38.302
two years is quite a long time.

570
00:35:49.105 --> 00:35:51.607
RYU GWANG-PIL
UNOFFICIAL REPORT

571
00:35:53.359 --> 00:35:54.861
RECORDING OF VICTIM INTERVIEW

572
00:35:59.115 --> 00:36:01.075
RYU GWANG-PIL
NOMINATION CORRUPTION REPORT

573
00:36:05.163 --> 00:36:06.289
<i>Are you crazy?</i>

574
00:36:06.372 --> 00:36:08.875
You and I are on the same side!

575
00:36:09.375 --> 00:36:12.128
We're in the same party. for fuck's sake!

576
00:36:12.211 --> 00:36:13.212
Assemblyman Ryu.

577
00:36:13.963 --> 00:36:17.300
There is no such thing as sides
when it comes to education.

578
00:36:17.383 --> 00:36:19.886
Was I your target from the very beginning?

579
00:36:19.969 --> 00:36:21.053
Just why?

580
00:36:21.137 --> 00:36:22.930
What the hell have I done so wrong?

581
00:36:23.514 --> 00:36:25.308
Are you serious or full of baloney?

582
00:36:26.100 --> 00:36:28.936
Your wrongdoings
should be all over the news by now.

583
00:36:31.355 --> 00:36:33.191
Shit. this is fucked up!

584
00:36:33.733 --> 00:36:36.068
There are so many people
worse than me out there!

585
00:36:36.569 --> 00:36:38.946
So why the hell are you doing this to me?

586
00:36:47.205 --> 00:36:49.457
That's because

587
00:36:50.416 --> 00:36:51.834
when you fall.

588
00:36:53.169 --> 00:36:54.754
your son falls too.

589
00:37:00.384 --> 00:37:04.680
You really should've educated
that brat of yours better.

590
00:37:17.109 --> 00:37:18.653
-Minister.
-Please step aside.

591
00:37:21.822 --> 00:37:23.032
Damn it!

592
00:37:23.115 --> 00:37:24.742
-Are you there?
-Sir!

593
00:37:25.743 --> 00:37:26.786
Just a moment!

594
00:37:26.869 --> 00:37:30.539
<i>The National Assembly approved</i>
<i>an arrest motion of Ryu Gwang-pil.</i>

595
00:37:30.623 --> 00:37:32.124
<i>who faces corruption allegations.</i>

596
00:37:32.708 --> 00:37:35.169
<i>Furthermore. there have been allegations</i>

597
00:37:35.253 --> 00:37:37.797
<i>that Ryu's son was responsible</i>
<i>for the school bullying</i>

598
00:37:37.880 --> 00:37:40.132
<i>that resulted</i>
<i>in the death of his classmate.</i>

599
00:37:40.216 --> 00:37:41.717
<i>shocking the public even more.</i>

600
00:37:41.801 --> 00:37:44.220
<i>This case. which almost got buried.</i>

601
00:37:44.303 --> 00:37:47.056
<i>surfaced through an investigation</i>
<i>by the ERPB.</i>

602
00:37:47.139 --> 00:37:51.352
{\an8}<i>The ERPB. a new agency</i>
<i>led by the Minister of Education.</i>

603
00:37:51.435 --> 00:37:54.814
<i>will handle the independent</i>
<i>and prompt protection of teachers' rights.</i>

604
00:37:54.897 --> 00:37:58.234
<i>It is responsible for receiving reports.</i>
<i>investigating. and responding--</i>

605
00:38:00.903 --> 00:38:03.572
This might also turn
into a political issue.

606
00:38:04.240 --> 00:38:05.283
Would you be okay?

607
00:38:05.366 --> 00:38:08.160
I'll take all the bullets and missiles.

608
00:38:08.869 --> 00:38:10.246
You just get the job done.

609
00:38:13.040 --> 00:38:15.293
Like you've ever been shot.

610
00:38:16.043 --> 00:38:18.713
If you get shot.
you'll actually die of pain.

611
00:38:19.964 --> 00:38:21.674
It's just a metaphor.

612
00:38:23.467 --> 00:38:24.635
I won't really take it.

613
00:38:24.719 --> 00:38:26.387
I was using a metaphor too.

614
00:38:26.470 --> 00:38:27.930
Thank you for your effort.

615
00:38:39.734 --> 00:38:41.861
Hey. did you guys see this?

616
00:38:41.944 --> 00:38:44.780
As of today. the Daehan High outcast is…

617
00:38:44.864 --> 00:38:47.700
Cutie Pie! Applause!

618
00:38:48.492 --> 00:38:50.786
Hey. it looks best on you so far.

619
00:38:54.540 --> 00:38:56.792
Our dear Jun-hyeong. where are you going?

620
00:38:57.293 --> 00:39:00.004
He's fucking nothing without his dad!

621
00:39:00.087 --> 00:39:01.630
It stinks like trash.

622
00:39:02.798 --> 00:39:05.926
OUTCAST STICK

623
00:39:52.515 --> 00:39:53.974
It's not your fault.

624
00:40:02.942 --> 00:40:04.026
Gyeong-min.

625
00:40:06.570 --> 00:40:07.988
It's not your fault.

626
00:40:17.456 --> 00:40:19.625
When Dae-seok became the outcast.

627
00:40:21.168 --> 00:40:22.837
I was relieved.

628
00:40:24.255 --> 00:40:25.589
When he died.

629
00:40:26.757 --> 00:40:28.259
I couldn't help but smile.

630
00:40:30.845 --> 00:40:34.014
I thought I'd be able to break free
from this hell.

631
00:40:38.894 --> 00:40:41.188
I'm no different from them.

632
00:40:44.483 --> 00:40:45.985
Yes. you are. kiddo.

633
00:40:47.820 --> 00:40:49.864
You were picked on for no reason.

634
00:40:50.573 --> 00:40:52.741
Those who bullied you

635
00:40:53.492 --> 00:40:57.204
and the adults who knew but silenced you
are the ones at fault.

636
00:40:57.830 --> 00:41:00.249
So don't be regretful

637
00:41:01.000 --> 00:41:02.209
or feel remorseful.

638
00:41:37.244 --> 00:41:39.330
-He's crazy!
-Fuck this!

639
00:41:39.413 --> 00:41:41.999
I recorded everything. you motherfucker.

640
00:41:42.500 --> 00:41:44.376
Die. you fucking bastards.

641
00:41:44.960 --> 00:41:46.170
Jun-hyeong!

642
00:41:46.253 --> 00:41:48.255
Jun-hyeong. I'm sorry!

643
00:41:48.339 --> 00:41:49.507
Jun-hyeong!

644
00:41:52.009 --> 00:41:53.302
Fuck this!

645
00:41:58.098 --> 00:41:59.475
-The ERPB is here.
-It's him.

646
00:41:59.558 --> 00:42:00.935
We're safe now.

647
00:42:01.519 --> 00:42:03.020
You just can't own up. can you?

648
00:42:08.692 --> 00:42:09.860
I told you. didn't I?

649
00:42:09.944 --> 00:42:13.447
Remorse is something you do
with your body. not your mind.

650
00:42:17.201 --> 00:42:18.035
Are you crazy?

651
00:42:18.118 --> 00:42:19.745
The gasoline.

652
00:42:20.329 --> 00:42:21.330
What about it?

653
00:42:25.167 --> 00:42:26.544
Isn't this why you poured it?

654
00:43:04.498 --> 00:43:07.793
Please help me! I'm sorry!

655
00:43:09.461 --> 00:43:10.754
I was wrong!

656
00:43:11.463 --> 00:43:13.716
Please help me!

657
00:43:19.972 --> 00:43:21.557
Please help me!

658
00:43:21.640 --> 00:43:23.475
It's all my fault.

659
00:43:23.559 --> 00:43:25.769
I'm sorry!

660
00:43:45.331 --> 00:43:48.500
Why the hell are you taking it
this far with me? Why?

661
00:43:49.084 --> 00:43:50.252
And what about you?

662
00:43:51.170 --> 00:43:53.547
Why did you take it so far with Dae-seok?

663
00:44:01.639 --> 00:44:03.849
Dae-seok was afraid of dying too.

664
00:44:04.391 --> 00:44:05.225
Just like you.

665
00:44:07.436 --> 00:44:09.146
But he still made that choice

666
00:44:09.647 --> 00:44:11.940
because of a scumbag like you.

667
00:44:14.068 --> 00:44:18.072
WITH VIGOR. HOLDING HOPEFUL DREAMS CLOSE

668
00:44:25.037 --> 00:44:27.748
<i>If you're finding the bullying</i>
<i>so difficult to deal with.</i>

669
00:44:27.831 --> 00:44:29.667
how about moving to a different school?

670
00:44:29.750 --> 00:44:32.503
Excuse me?
Why should my child move to a new school?

671
00:44:33.545 --> 00:44:37.466
<i>The bully should switch schools.</i>
<i>Why should the victim go?</i>

672
00:44:40.219 --> 00:44:43.514
You can't just cancel your order
all of a sudden like this.

673
00:44:43.597 --> 00:44:46.850
I just don't understand what's going on
with our vendors.

674
00:44:48.769 --> 00:44:49.978
I'm sorry.

675
00:44:50.062 --> 00:44:51.730
-Please go easy on my dad.
-Get lost.

676
00:44:51.814 --> 00:44:53.399
-Shut up.
-Ask your dad.

677
00:44:53.482 --> 00:44:55.442
Ask him to go easy on my dad
this one time.

678
00:44:55.526 --> 00:44:59.238
Why are you asking me?
I'm just a helpless jerk without my dad.

679
00:44:59.321 --> 00:45:00.698
I'm really sorry.

680
00:45:00.781 --> 00:45:04.284
What can I do to make it up to you?
I'll do whatever you say.

681
00:45:06.787 --> 00:45:08.163
Go fucking die. then.

682
00:45:32.312 --> 00:45:35.357
Making the students
realize the full extent of their actions

683
00:45:35.441 --> 00:45:38.944
by giving them
a taste of their own medicine

684
00:45:39.027 --> 00:45:41.780
and making them take responsibility
for those actions.

685
00:45:42.322 --> 00:45:44.616
This is the true education…

686
00:45:46.702 --> 00:45:48.662
that the ERPB seeks.

687
00:45:59.339 --> 00:46:01.675
But no matter what you do to make amends…

688
00:46:04.303 --> 00:46:06.472
Dae-seok
can never be brought back to life.

689
00:46:08.682 --> 00:46:11.977
The least you can do is carry that burden
for the rest of your life.

690
00:46:13.395 --> 00:46:15.397
That's the only way to make it fair.

691
00:46:21.487 --> 00:46:23.238
This is the hell you created.

692
00:46:23.322 --> 00:46:24.907
See how you like living there.

693
00:46:41.089 --> 00:46:43.592
<i>The police reopened Dae-seok's case</i>

694
00:46:43.675 --> 00:46:46.720
<i>and arrested those who bullied Dae-seok.</i>
<i>including Ryu Jun-hyeong.</i>

695
00:46:46.804 --> 00:46:49.223
You told me to trust you.
you fucking bitch!

696
00:46:49.306 --> 00:46:50.516
<i>And for the first time…</i>

697
00:46:50.599 --> 00:46:51.558
He's not here.

698
00:46:51.642 --> 00:46:53.936
<i>…the principal took accountability</i>
<i>like a grown-up.</i>

699
00:46:54.019 --> 00:46:55.521
-I said he's not here.
-Mr. Kim!

700
00:46:55.604 --> 00:46:57.064
What are you doing down there?

701
00:46:58.190 --> 00:47:00.150
<i>On the ERPB website.</i>

702
00:47:00.234 --> 00:47:03.737
<i>Ryu Jun-hyeong's bullying</i>
<i>was made public for everyone to see.</i>

703
00:47:07.491 --> 00:47:11.370
<i>And they say those records</i>
<i>will never be erased</i>

704
00:47:11.453 --> 00:47:13.664
<i>unless the victims forgive them.</i>

705
00:47:17.584 --> 00:47:20.879
<i>That was how the ERPB</i>
<i>ended their guidance at Daehan High.</i>

706
00:47:26.426 --> 00:47:30.222
<i>After that day. we never saw</i>
<i>the inspector at school again.</i>

707
00:48:38.832 --> 00:48:41.293
THE LATE CHOI GA-YUN
1995.07.25 - 2024.11.27

708
00:48:41.376 --> 00:48:43.670
WE WILL NOT FORGET

709
00:50:33.697 --> 00:50:38.702
Subtitle translation by: Lisa Kim
